snippet.title: Divinity II: Ego Draconis Complete Cinematic Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
Complete Cinematic Trailer (acts 1+2+3) in one single video. It unveils a small extract of the story behind Divinity 2.
The video contained subtitles. Make sure to activate them if you are interested in watching.
